    ⚡ HOW THE PROGRAM WORKS:
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

    🔹 CORE TECHNOLOGY

    Microsoft Activation Scripts operate through Windows command-line scripting and PowerShell automation.  
    The script communicates with Windows licensing services to retrieve activation status, apply activation methods, and configure licensing parameters.

    The system automatically detects the installed version of Windows or Office and then provides the appropriate activation options.  
    All operations are executed through built-in Windows licensing components without requiring heavy background services.

    The script interface guides users step-by-step through activation options while displaying real-time status information.


